---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro'
import { withBase } from '../lib/url'
---

<Base
  title="about · meshblog"
  description="Who built meshblog, what the coined terms mean, and why it is built this way."
  topBarActive="about"
>
  <article class="about-layout" id="about">
    <!-- ── Header ──────────────────────────────────────────────── -->
    <header class="about-header">
      <div class="eyebrow">about · 소개</div>
      <h1>meshblog</h1>
      <p class="sub">
        Jaeyeon Bang의 이중언어 독서실 — 두 번째 뇌를 공개합니다.
      </p>
    </header>

    <!-- ── Opening stanza ─────────────────────────────────────── -->
    <section class="about-section">
      <p class="about-body">
        meshblog is Jaeyeon Bang's bilingual reading room — a second brain compiled into a public site.
        Written in Korean and English, cross-linked in both.
        meshblog는 재연 방의 이중언어 독서실입니다. 두 언어로 쓰고, 두 언어로 연결합니다.
      </p>
    </section>

    <!-- ── Coined terms glossary ───────────────────────────────── -->
    <section class="about-section" id="glossary" aria-labelledby="glossary-heading">
      <h2 class="section-eyebrow" id="glossary-heading">Coined terms · 용어</h2>
      <dl class="glossary">
        <div class="gloss-entry">
          <dt><strong>vault</strong> <span class="gloss-ko">볼트</span></dt>
          <dd>
            The full collection of notes. Obsidian's term; here it means everything under
            <code>content/notes/</code>. Think of it as the raw filing cabinet — every note lives here
            before it is published.
          </dd>
        </div>

        <div class="gloss-entry">
          <dt><strong>concept mesh</strong> <span class="gloss-ko">개념 메시</span></dt>
          <dd>
            The second-order graph — not the notes themselves, but the concepts extracted from them.
            Shown on the home sidebar and accessible at <a href={withBase('/graph?mode=concept')}>graph · concept mode</a>.
            Where the vault is a filing cabinet, the concept mesh is the index of ideas pinned to a corkboard.
          </dd>
        </div>

        <div class="gloss-entry">
          <dt><strong>backlinks</strong> <span class="gloss-ko">역링크</span></dt>
          <dd>
            Inbound wikilinks — who pointed here. If Note A links to Note B, then Note B's backlinks include A.
            Visible in the reader aside on every note page, and as a dedicated graph mode at
            <a href={withBase('/graph?mode=backlinks')}>graph · backlinks</a>.
          </dd>
        </div>

        <div class="gloss-entry">
          <dt>
            <strong>L1 · 직접</strong> &nbsp;/&nbsp;
            <strong>L2 · 근처</strong> &nbsp;/&nbsp;
            <strong>L3 · 클러스터</strong>
          </dt>
          <dd>
            Graph depth. L1 shows direct links only (immediate neighbors of the selected node).
            L2 shows two-hop neighbors — neighbors of neighbors.
            L3 shows the full community cluster the node belongs to.
            Toggle depth with the seg buttons in the <a href={withBase('/graph')}>graph</a> controls bar.
          </dd>
        </div>

        <div class="gloss-entry">
          <dt><strong>knowledge mesh</strong> <span class="gloss-ko">지식 메시</span></dt>
          <dd>
            The full graph of notes + concepts + backlinks combined. Accessible at
            <a href={withBase('/graph')}>graph</a>. It is the whole web — every node and every edge
            in the vault — rendered as a navigable canvas.
          </dd>
        </div>

        <div class="gloss-entry">
          <dt><strong>ask the vault</strong> <span class="gloss-ko">볼트에 묻기</span></dt>
          <dd>
            The command-K search palette — type any phrase and it answers across notes and Q&amp;A cards.
            Keyboard shortcut: <kbd>⌘K</kbd> on macOS or <kbd>Ctrl+K</kbd> on Windows/Linux.
            검색은 SQLite full-text, 의미 매칭은 OpenAI 임베딩(키가 있을 때). 둘 다 로컬 볼트에서 돈다.
          </dd>
        </div>
      </dl>
    </section>

    <!-- ── Why it's built this way ────────────────────────────── -->
    <section class="about-section" aria-labelledby="why-heading">
      <h2 class="section-eyebrow" id="why-heading">Why it's built this way · 이렇게 만든 이유</h2>
      <p class="about-body">
        meshblog is an AI-native daily-repair harness for Obsidian power users — a fork-and-use
        open-source template. Every night a GitHub Action reviews the vault: broken wikilinks,
        draft notes that leaked to <code>main</code>, stale backlink caches. It opens a pull request
        with a Markdown report, so the vault repairs itself while you sleep.
        This is what separates meshblog from Obsidian Publish or Quartz — those tools ship your notes
        once. meshblog ships them and then watches them.
      </p>
    </section>

    <!-- ── Colophon ────────────────────────────────────────────── -->
    <section class="about-section" id="colophon" aria-labelledby="colophon-heading">
      <h2 class="section-eyebrow" id="colophon-heading">Colophon · 콜로폰</h2>
      <dl class="colophon-list">
        <div class="coloph-entry">
          <dt>Typefaces</dt>
          <dd>
            <a href="https://fonts.adobe.com/fonts/source-serif" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Source Serif 4</a>
            (display &amp; body) ·
            <a href="https://fonts.google.com/noto/specimen/Noto+Serif+KR" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Noto Serif KR</a>
            (Korean) ·
            Pretendard (UI sans) ·
            <a href="https://www.jetbrains.com/lp/mono/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">JetBrains Mono</a>
            (code &amp; labels)
          </dd>
        </div>

        <div class="coloph-entry">
          <dt>Stack</dt>
          <dd>
            <a href="https://astro.build" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Astro</a> (static site) ·
            SQLite (local embeddings store) ·
            OpenAI embeddings (semantic search — degrades gracefully when key is absent) ·
            <a href="https://graphology.github.io" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Graphology</a>
            (graph data structure) · Deployed via GitHub Pages
          </dd>
        </div>

        <div class="coloph-entry">
          <dt>Source</dt>
          <dd>
            <a href="https://github.com/JaeyeonBang/meshblog" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
              github.com/JaeyeonBang/meshblog
            </a>
            — MIT license. Fork it, point it at your own Obsidian vault, run <code>claude /init</code>.
          </dd>
        </div>
      </dl>
    </section>
  </article>
</Base>

<style>
  /* ── About layout ──────────────────────────────────────────── */
  .about-layout {
    max-width: 60ch;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 var(--space-8) var(--space-24);
  }

  /* ── Header ────────────────────────────────────────────────── */
  .about-header {
    padding: var(--space-12) 0 var(--space-10);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--ink);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-10);
  }

  .eyebrow {
    font-family: var(--f-mono);
    font-size: var(--fs-xs);
    letter-spacing: var(--track-eyebrow);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--ink-3);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-5);
  }

  .about-header h1 {
    font-family: var(--f-disp);
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: var(--fs-5xl);
    margin: 0 0 var(--space-5);
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    line-height: 1;
    font-variation-settings: "opsz" 144;
  }

  .about-header .sub {
    font-family: var(--f-serif);
    font-size: var(--fs-xl);
    color: var(--ink-2);
    line-height: 1.5;
    margin: 0;
    font-weight: 400;
  }

  /* ── Sections ──────────────────────────────────────────────── */
  .about-section {
    padding: var(--space-8) 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--ink-5);
  }

  .about-section:last-child {
    border-bottom: 0;
  }

  .section-eyebrow {
    font-family: var(--f-mono);
    font-size: var(--fs-xs);
    letter-spacing: var(--track-eyebrow);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--ink-3);
    margin: 0 0 var(--space-6);
    font-weight: 400;
  }

  .about-body {
    font-family: var(--f-serif);
    font-size: var(--fs-lg);
    color: var(--ink-2);
    line-height: 1.65;
    margin: 0;
  }

  /* ── Glossary ──────────────────────────────────────────────── */
  .glossary {
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0;
  }

  .gloss-entry {
    padding: var(--space-5) 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--ink-5);
  }

  .gloss-entry:last-child {
    border-bottom: 0;
    padding-bottom: 0;
  }

  .glossary dt {
    font-family: var(--f-disp);
    font-size: var(--fs-lg);
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--ink);
    margin: 0 0 var(--space-2);
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
  }

  .glossary dt strong {
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .gloss-ko {
    font-family: var(--f-mono);
    font-size: var(--fs-xs);
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    color: var(--ink-3);
    font-weight: 400;
    margin-left: var(--space-2);
  }

  .glossary dd {
    font-family: var(--f-serif);
    font-size: var(--fs-base);
    color: var(--ink-2);
    line-height: 1.65;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .glossary dd a {
    color: var(--ink);
    text-decoration: underline;
    text-underline-offset: 3px;
  }

  .glossary dd a:hover {
    background: var(--ink);
    color: var(--paper);
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  /* ── Colophon ──────────────────────────────────────────────── */
  .colophon-list {
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0;
  }

  .coloph-entry {
    padding: var(--space-4) 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--ink-5);
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 8ch 1fr;
    gap: var(--space-4);
    align-items: baseline;
  }

  .coloph-entry:last-child {
    border-bottom: 0;
  }

  .colophon-list dt {
    font-family: var(--f-mono);
    font-size: var(--fs-xs);
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--ink-3);
    margin: 0;
    padding-top: 2px;
  }

  .colophon-list dd {
    font-family: var(--f-serif);
    font-size: var(--fs-sm);
    color: var(--ink-2);
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .colophon-list dd a {
    color: var(--ink);
    text-decoration: underline;
    text-underline-offset: 3px;
  }

  .colophon-list dd a:hover {
    background: var(--ink);
    color: var(--paper);
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  /* ── Inline code ───────────────────────────────────────────── */
  code {
    font-family: var(--f-mono);
    font-size: var(--fs-xs);
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
    color: var(--ink-3);
    background: var(--paper-2);
    padding: 2px 5px;
    border: 1px solid var(--ink-5);
  }

  /* ── Kbd ───────────────────────────────────────────────────── */
  kbd {
    font-family: var(--f-mono);
    font-size: var(--fs-xs);
    padding: 2px 6px;
    color: var(--ink);
    background: var(--paper);
    border: 1px solid var(--ink-5);
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
  }

  /* ── Responsive ────────────────────────────────────────────── */
  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .about-layout {
      padding: 0 var(--space-5) var(--space-16);
    }

    .coloph-entry {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: var(--space-2);
    }
  }
</style>
